{"tid":1547633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[831太子恐襲]被警察圍之前示威者識行識走(有片)","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:33:03.000Z","uid":206090,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27d1b08e8c556a022bd1134a6d93f913c429cfdc","tid":1547633,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ten567KT16o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dten567KT16o&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2reFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=41c116d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ten567KT16o</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我係剪輯以上影片既巴打。</span><br />\n<br />\n831當晚有示威者比大量警察圍住，完全唔比記者影，好多人都估係咪圍住做急救，甚至依家不停流傳有人死。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4Xp9dLJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Xp9dLJ.png&h=425e467d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過我Study過自已條片之後(係, 條片自已剪都要再study, 因為資訊量實在太多)，其實比大量警察圍住既有3個男士，1個係著黑色Puma短褲(就係懷疑被人打暈，之後兩個速龍眼望望嗰位被制服既男士)，1個係著白拖鞋白衫黑長褲既，另外1個就係被壓頸既男士(網上流傳個條片個位)。<br />\n<br />\n頭2名男士係比警察押解之下自行行去大量警察圍的位置，個時仲識行識走，上面條片其實有影到，大家不妨細心d睇下。而第三個男士係無被移動過，佢就係係大量警察圍的位置被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>稍後我會拍條片解釋返。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>希望各位唔會因為網上一D過度解讀、講到似層層真係有人死既言論，就&ldquo;盲目地完全相信&rdquo;而作無謂嘅犧牲或者過激行為。</strong><br />\n當然大家要繼續爭取港鐵公開CCTV，揭露警察嘅暴行！香港人加油！"},{"pid":"b8b0c5e0f36fb09c5c13cc4279129040efa2de69","tid":1547633,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"4f7e26ce151a50ec9ea7b4f9a2d2eb5a18d2eda9","tid":1547633,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afc9419cb6f237a52596173947aad08ee69c5d1","tid":1547633,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你班仆街肯接受現實未?<br />\n你覺得最近一日死咁多人喺巧合?<br />\n屌你老母 我真喺唔撚信唔關831事<br />\n唔喺831 咁新屋嶺呢?<br />\n今日軍營張相呢?武警嚟架傻閪!<br />\n醒下啦香港人! </span></span><br />\n<br />\nbtw 推此post"},{"pid":"f1591b9886816c7218ae3c34f0e687f30bd7d2c4","tid":1547633,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cWpmiVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWpmiVy.jpg&h=5540436c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/zqni5ts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzqni5ts.jpg&h=45208923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1AfwFVb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AfwFVb.png&h=caa19c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/v24YkVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv24YkVF.jpg&h=57435ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8d9abfddcb333ceee69870b54ef30351b11a2bc","tid":1547633,"uid":303291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T23:20:56.000Z","msg":"樓主條片剪得好好<br />\n我覺得圍困係牆邊的人<br />\n只能肯定被壓頸係其中之一<br />\npuma褲同拖鞋男我知道樓主指邊2個<br />\n不過puma褲好似影唔到佢最終停左係邊<br />\n而拖鞋男被押去同一方向時<br />\n好似無停留係果段牆邊<br />\n直接押去車尾方向<br />\n你段片6:51隱約見到有個白衫人<br />\n我覺得就係拖鞋男<br />\n不過當時電筒一直閃加埋個鏡頭移動緊<br />\n所以都唔能夠肯定<br />\n我覺得其他被困係牆邊的人之中<br />\n應該有部分被扑時無人影到"},{"pid":"4b6e35ea8c99c7658d9281aeff42ce51e7d42